 Joni Mitchell 的音乐终于回归 Spotify https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchells-music-is-finally-back-on-spotify-3607919?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=joni-mitchells-music-is-finally-back-现场Surej SinghFri, 22 Mar 2024 03:11:41 +0000 Music NewsNewsFolkhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3607919 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她宣布将于 2022 年从流媒体平台上删除自己的音乐，以声援尼尔·杨 (Neil Young) 因乔·罗根 (Joe Rogan) 有争议的播客而发表的言论</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchells-music-is-finally-back-on-spotify-3607919">Joni Mitchell 的音乐终于回归 Spotify 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a>的音乐终于再次在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>上发布。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/joni-mitchells-court-and-spark-at-50-3577635">乔尼·米切尔 (Joni Mitchell) 50 岁时的《Court And Spark》：“她是我们这一代人中的每个人都很酷的阿姨”</a></strong></li></ul><p>两年前，米切尔宣布将从<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-removes-catalogue-from-spotify-in-solidarity-with-neil-young-3149464">流媒体巨头 Spotify 上删除她的整个目录，以声援</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young">Neil Young</a> ，此前 Neil Young <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-wants-his-music-removed-from-spotify-immediately-citing-false-information-about-vaccines-3145688">从该平台撤回了自己的音乐，以抗议该服务平台散布有关 COVID-19 疫苗的错误信息</a>。</p><p>截至今天（3月22日），米切尔的音乐已经恢复，距离<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-announces-return-to-spotify-3600314">Young宣布重返平台</a>还不到两周。米切尔尚未就她重返该平台公开发表评论。</p><p> 2022 年 1 月，Young 宣布退出 Spotify，原因是担心这家流媒体巨头提供“不负责任”的播客，例如<em>《The Joe Rogan Experience》，</em>传播有关 COVID-19 疫苗的错误信息。不久之后，米切尔<a href="https://jonimitchell.com/news/newsitem.cfm?id=1592">在她的网站上分享了一份声明</a>，宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-removes-catalogue-from-spotify-in-solidarity-with-neil-young-3149464">她将追随杨的脚步</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3580421" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3580421" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3580421" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3580421" class="wp-caption-text">乔尼·米切尔 (Joni Mitchell) 现场表演，2023 年。图片来源：Gary Miller/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>虽然她没有点名罗根——当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-rogan-signs-with-spotify-for-exclusive-podcast-deal-2672515">罗根与 Spotify 签订了价值 1 亿美元的独家合同</a>——但她确实分享了一封公开信的链接，该公开信是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/270-scientists-write-letter-to-spotify-on-joe-rogans-dangerous-covid-misinformation-3136969">数百名科学家和医学专业人士</a>在罗根的播客上猛烈抨击的。</p><p> “我决定从 Spotify 上删除我的所有音乐，”米切尔当时写道。 “不负责任的人散布谎言，导致人们丧生。在这个问题上，我与尼尔·杨以及全球科学界和医学界站在一起。”</p><p><em>乔·罗根体验 (Joe Rogan Experience)</em>对 Spotify 的独占权已结束，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/apple">苹果</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/amazon">亚马逊</a>收购，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-announces-return-to-spotify-3600314">促使杨重返 Spotify</a> 。 <a href="https://neilyoungarchives.com/news/1/article?id=MY%20RETURN%20TO%20LOW%20RES%20SPOTIFY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">本月早些时候，Young 在他的网站上的一篇文章中写道</a>：“Spotify，世界上排名第一的低分辨率音乐流媒体 - Spotify 的质量比我们低，现在将再次成为我的音乐之家。”</p><p>他继续解释道：“我的决定是在苹果和亚马逊音乐服务商开始提供我在 Spotify 所反对的虚假信息播客功能之际做出的。我不能像离开 Spotify 那样离开苹果和亚马逊，因为我的音乐对于音乐爱好者来说几乎没有什么流媒体渠道。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchells-music-is-finally-back-on-spotify-3607919">Joni Mitchell 的音乐终于回归 Spotify 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
